track.name: All Or Nothing At All
comments: Dallas had this little jazz club called "Froggy Bottoms", and Diana would've set the place on fire.
Yes  she  has  that  raspy  kind  of  bluesy  voice that  sound  so  smooth  for  this  kind  of  jazzy   music
I'm with yarom1. One of my favorites from her. Sunday morning coffee.

What a gift we have in this girl !!     she is quite outstanding and fits in with late nite listening ......... and her back up musical arrangement? ........ I thought we didn't make 'em like this any more....... how happy I am to be so wrong !!
They must have been happy when they heard the final recording !
That back-up band is kick'n ace
